subject: Tennis
Wimbledon Tennis Tournament
lead_paragraph: The defending champion Justine Henin defeated second-seeded Amélie Mauresmo yesterday, 7-5, 6-7 (4), 7-6 (2), in the final of the Eastbourne International in England.
